Titolo: Anvil of Dawn

Anno: 1995

Descrizione: Anvil of Dawn is a 1995 fantasy role-playing video game developed by DreamForge Intertainment and published by New World Computing.  Anvil of Dawn was named the best role-playing game of 1995 by Computer Gaming World and Computer Game Review. In 2013, the game was re-released via GOG.com with Microsoft Windows support.